  "valid_count": 4,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q1",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q1\"\n    title=\"Identificación del origen en coordenadas\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>D</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un plano cartesiano se representa una plaza. El origen del plano, el punto\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, corresponde a la entrada principal.</p>\n    <p>La siguiente tabla muestra las coordenadas de cuatro bancos de la plaza.</p>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Punto</th>\n          <th>Coordenadas\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Punto A</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Punto B</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Punto C</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Punto D</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>¿Cuál de estos puntos está ubicado exactamente en la entrada principal de la plaza?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        Punto A\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Punto B\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        Punto C\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        Punto D\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q7",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\" identifier=\"A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q7\" title=\"Localización de puntos en plano cartesiano (tabla de refugios)\" adaptive=\"false\" time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un plano cartesiano se representa un croquis de cuatro refugios de montaña respecto del centro de un valle ubicado en el origen. Las coordenadas se expresan como \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, donde los valores positivos de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math> indican este y los negativos oeste; los valores positivos de \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math> indican norte y los negativos sur.</p>\n    <p>La tabla muestra las coordenadas de cada refugio (en km):</p>\n    <table>\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Refugio</th>\n          <th>Coordenadas \n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mi>x</mi>\n                <mo>,</mo>\n                <mi>y</mi>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td>R</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>6</mn>\n                <mo>,</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>S</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>6</mn>\n                <mo>,</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>T</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mo>,</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>U</td>\n          <td>\n            <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n              <mrow>\n                <mo>(</mo>\n                <mo>-</mo>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mo>,</mo>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n                <mo>)</mo>\n              </mrow>\n            </math>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>¿Cuál refugio está más al oeste que el refugio T, tiene la misma coordenada en \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math> que el refugio T y se ubica en el tercer cuadrante?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">Refugio R.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">Refugio S.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">Refugio T.</qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">Refugio U.</qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q8",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q8\"\n    title=\"Punto más lejano del origen\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En el plano cartesiano se consideran cuatro puntos cuyas coordenadas están dadas en la forma \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mi>y</mi>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>,\n      medidas desde el origen \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mn>0</mn>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de estos puntos está más lejos del origen?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\" max-choices=\"1\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>6</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q13",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-GEO-03-02_Q13\"\n    title=\"Coordenadas del cuarto vértice de un rectángulo\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un plano cartesiano se representa el croquis de un pequeño jardín rectangular. Tres de sus esquinas tienen las siguientes coordenadas: A\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, B\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      y C\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>(</mo>\n          <mn>4</mn>\n          <mo>,</mo>\n          <mo>-</mo>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo>)</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuáles son las coordenadas de la cuarta esquina del jardín?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mo>(</mo>\n            <mo>-</mo>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n            <mo>,</mo>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mo>)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 13
    }
  ]
